description:
What exactly is Creation Sabbath?

Since we are Christians who believe in the Bible, this is not a debate but rather a celebration. It is the day of rest known as the Sabbath, which is holy to the Lord. This is a time for us to think about who we are in God, how we relate to others, and how we relate to God. There is always something new to learn on the Sabbath, and it's a good time to think about how faith and science are connected.

Watch the video to learn more about Creation Sabbath, which our world church observes every fourth Sabbath of October.



https://youtu.be/gba7BbPjGUA
